Package: PDscripting
Title: Functions to faciliate running PD scripting node scripts
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Randy", "Johnson", email = "randall.johnson@nih.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains functions to facilitate wrangling of PD scripting node files and output, as well as other functions we find useful for post-PD analysis (e.g. filtering by condition).
